{"tid":1858576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實中國北方3個月前已爆緊鼠疫(黑死病) 大家要有心理準備","createTime":"2020-02-02T19:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T20:07:46.000Z","uid":125193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aca6f5e209bdc5a6506e1f64d1e38d0d82179451","tid":1858576,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T19:16:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200107/IW7HAE63GABBLXWWNI7TMWFEU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200107%2FIW7HAE63GABBLXWWNI7TMWFEU4%2F&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VwVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=e378b53e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200107%2FIW7HAE63GABBLXWWNI7TMWFEU4%2F&h=0edaca79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200107/IW7HAE63GABBLXWWNI7TMWFEU4/</a><br />\n<br />\n內地近期爆發鼠疫個案，令本港也現疫症危機。傳染病專家表示，鼠疫桿菌主要經被蝨咬即跳蚤叮咬傳人，感染若嚴重可入血、入肺，致命率高達6成勿忽視，呼籲市民避免到高發地區如內蒙古，或揀選入住衞生良好的住宿地方及做好防蝨工作，又不排除本港稍後或有零星個案，要提高警覺，包括返港後有咳嗽、淋巴腺腫脹等症狀要及早求醫。<br />\n<br />\n記者：梁麗兒<br />\n內地去年截至11月29日通報有4宗鼠疫個案，包括內蒙古有2宗腺鼠疫個案，及北京2宗肺鼠疫個案，也涉及內蒙古一對夫婦。感染及傳染病科專科醫生曾祈殷表示，與近幾年西非、馬達加斯加的鼠疫疫情相比，內地未算大型爆發，而且出現相關風險也不大，關鍵是要及早截斷傳播源頭，做好消滅跳蚤的工作。由於兩地人流交往頻繁，不排除本港稍後有零星個案出現。<br />\n<br />\n曾指，不少港人喜歡到內蒙、甘肅及青海等已出現鼠疫確診或被傳有懷疑個案的地區旅遊，故前往當地有一定受感染風險，建議最好避免前往，或抵達後遠離疫區。若必要去須小心選擇住宿的地方，包括要有良好衞生、遠離街市。在戶外要避免接觸野生動物，尤其動物屍體包括死老鼠，應避免吃野味，或到賣野味的地方。由於鼠疫潛伏期可長達7日，有關人士若回港後有咳嗽、咳出帶血的痰、發燒及淋巴腫脹等懷疑症狀，要盡快求醫，並將旅遊史告知醫生，包括曾否被跳蚤叮咬。<br />\n<br />\n現在係無左消息!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b756fb696676908fa37230286c31c7a5b3a15b8e","tid":1858576,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T19:18:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-50409031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-50409031&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VwVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=0ec536a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-50409031</a>"},{"pid":"d157195df8b4d834110325ca47b7125111249088","tid":1858576,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T19:24:53.000Z","msg":"依家鼠疫有得醫<br />\n其實已經冇咩殺傷力"},{"pid":"44dafed71dfe4645aed224628e3e8926f5d616e4","tid":1858576,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T19:25:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1d89401cc943bf97ddd4d0136fdadb21ffbbafa9","tid":1858576,"uid":113155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T19:49:18.000Z","msg":"唔係冇，係武漢肺炎哩單太大，蓋過咗鼠疫。<br />\n點止鼠疫，仲有豬瘟，雞瘟，地震。<br />\n天都睇唔過眼。"},{"pid":"a0a9055e67ccc0a71a254a8de5b0596ea9314605","tid":1858576,"uid":7704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T19:55:48.000Z","msg":"支那真係好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30a204feb55f0cb0f1722ec5e23300f25383c81","tid":1858576,"uid":178187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T20:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TYGV29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TYGV29.png&h=947e6029&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c9db40f94ef1309ec9010a30e5d9fa5a89e2a94","tid":1858576,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T20:06:51.000Z","msg":"到底中共係唔係實施緊減少人口政策？"},{"pid":"5e2dc69094938d323aa006ccbc54d5f1ca28f6a8","tid":1858576,"uid":19260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c9db40f94ef1309ec9010a30e5d9fa5a89e2a94","tid":1858576,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T20:06:51.000Z","msg":"到底中共係唔係實施緊減少人口政策？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T20:07:46.000Z","msg":"2020滅貧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}